{
  "title": "O sowal no ’Amis",
  "titleCh": "阿美族語",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "阿美族語分為五個語別，分別是南勢阿美語、秀姑巒阿美語、海岸阿美語、馬蘭阿美語及恆春阿美語。這是早期日本研究學者所做的劃分。我們阿美族袓先的想法不是這樣，他們是以部落為主體。太巴塱人的部落在太巴塱，他們所說的語言是太巴塱語。\r\n[---]\r\n秀姑巒阿美語系內的馬太鞍、太巴塱、璞石閣、富源、豐濱仍然有語言上的差異。例如，豐濱人稱酒瓶為「talid」；馬太鞍人叫「kofoc」；太巴塱人叫「katopih」；富源人叫「tingalaway」。",
      "ab": "Pakini i sowal no ’Amis i, limaay ko kasasiroma no kasa’etal. O no ’amisay, o no Siwkolanay, o no Pasawaliay, o no Farangaway ato no Paridaway. Oni a kakakonis i, o sa’osi no mikingkiway no Dipong itiya ho. O harateng no malitengay ita o ’Amis i, caay ka matira, o niyaro’ ko pinangan no sowal. \r\n[===]\r\nI Tafalongay a tamdaw i, i Tafalong ko niyaro’, o no Tafalong ko sowal nangra. I salaloma’ no kasae’tal no Siwkolan, ira ho ko kasasiroma no sowal no Fata’an, no Tafalong, no Posko, no Pa’ilasen ato no Fakong. Tinako to talid hananay no Fakongay, o kofoc han no i Fata’anay, o katopih han no i Tafalongay, o tingalaway han no Pa’ilasen.",
      "order": "1",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2021/03/31/510b6f55b4e82a73b48635536b5a47f6.wav",
